{"tid":1318775,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「獅子狗」事件續發酵 沙田吉野家變連儂牆","createTime":"2019-07-15T04:22:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T04:22:27.000Z","uid":241764,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"323f88917571af10c1aa0b4a46893883ca2ed9ba","tid":1318775,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T04:22:27.000Z","msg":"《逃犯條例》爭議持續，因「獅子狗」廣告而陷入「公關災難」的吉野家，其沙田好運中心分店昨日以巨型木板圍封外牆玻璃，嚴陣以待，以免遭到破壞。記者今早再到現場，發現木板已變成連儂牆，貼上各式標貼和海報，部分寫有「撤回惡法」、「黑警」等字句。<br />\n<br />\n吉野家日前在Facebook「抽水」發文，圖中出現「唔准叫我獅子狗」的字句，向網民解釋其食品是「竹輪」。擁有香港吉野家經營權的香港合興集團有限公司，總裁洪明基向傳媒表示已解僱負責廣告事務的公司員工。不過吉野家Facebook其後發文，稱所有小編都繼續工作，暗示該名發帖文的小編沒有被解僱。<br />\n<br />\n事件源於警方早前清走涉及警員個人資料的相關標貼後，被網民揶揄為「撕紙狗」，其後吉野家於Facebook發圖文，稱「唔准叫我獅子狗」，指正「獅子狗」為日本食品「竹輪」，引起網民瘋傳。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20190715/_2019071510581354081.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20190715%2F_2019071510581354081.jpg&h=95655064&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20190715/_2019071510581155566.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20190715%2F_2019071510581155566.jpg&h=10992320&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20190715/_2019071510581412637.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20190715%2F_2019071510581412637.jpg&h=4a81401d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20190715/_2019071510581531427.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20190715%2F_2019071510581531427.jpg&h=f140a578&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/1044395-%E9%A6%99%E6